"'''''Battle for the Golden Sun'''''" is a [[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]] adventure book for use with ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]''. The adventure scenario follows a special team of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] agents who volunteer for a mission to the legendary [[Waterworld/Legends|waterworld]] of [[Sedri/Legends|Sedri]] in search of a missing [[Mors Odrion|Alliance dignitary]] while trying to solve the mystery of the [[Golden Sun]].

The ''Battle for the Golden Sun'' set includes a full-color map of an [[Imperial Aquatic Garrison|Imperial Sea Garrison]]. ''Battle for the Golden Sun'' was written by [[Douglas Kaufman]] and published by [[West End Games]] in [[November]] [[1988]].

{{Book-stub}}

==Publisher's summary==
===Front cover===
''On an unexplored water [[Planet/Legends|planet]], warring natives, a missing [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] dignitary, [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] shock troops, and Rebel agents become entangled in the mystery of the [[Golden Sun]].''

===Back cover===
''A navigational accident has led the Empire to the mysterious and legendary water world of [[Sedri/Legends|Sedri]]. Rebel spy networks carry troubling tales back to [[Alliance High Command/Legends|Alliance High Command]], rumors that Sedri holds the secret of the Golden Sun — a secret that could give the Empire the power to crush the Rebellion once and for all!''

''An Alliance dignitary, young and impetuous, disappeared while checking into these disturbing rumors. Now a special team of Rebel agents volunteer to undertake a desperate mission. Guided by a half-sane [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]], they must make their way to Sedri, locate the missing dignitary, avoid Imperial entanglements, and solve the mystery of the Golden Sun.''

''If the rumors prove even partially true, then this band of Rebels is all that stands between the Empire and total control of the Galaxy&hellip;''

'''40-page booklet features:'''
*''An exciting script with a part for each player that brings their characters to life and plunges them right into the action.''
*''Detailed descriptions and maps of an underwater village and the mysterious [[Sun caves|Sun Caves of Sedri]]''.
*''Background information on a new race of sea dwellers from the planet Sedri.''
*''A pull-out section full of colorful non-player character templates for an added dimension in roleplaying excitement.''

'''Also includes:'''
*''A poster-size, full color map of an [[Imperial Aquatic Garrison]] - a complete base with descriptions of important areas, special equipment, and undersea stormtroopers.''
*''Extensive guidelines to help gamemasters make their adventures fast-moving, challenging and fun.''

'''''A complete adventure for ''Star Wars: The Roleplaying Rame''. For gamemaster and one or more players.'''''

